  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Team Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are a centrally located boutique firm experiencing strong growth. As the company scales, we are looking to bring on a Internal Recruitment Manager to develop strategic plans and system implementation to support through the next phase of growth and development roadmap.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will be responsible for:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead and coach a team of recruitment consultants in achieving sales targets and company objectives</li>\n  <li>Manage the end-to-end recruitment process with a team of consultants</li>\n  <li>Build new business relationships and maintain good rapport with existing clients</li>\n  <li>Maintain efficient day-to-day operations in line with company protocol</li>\n  <li>Work closely with company management to provide market insights and feedback for decision-making</li>\n  <li>Improve on current process and implementing new business processes and procedures</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties may apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 3 years of relevant experience (Preferably in the Recruitment Staffing industry)</li>\n  <li>Strong business acumen, analytical skills and use of data to advice on key business insights</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or <strong>email </strong>an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 19C9682</p>\n<p><br></p>",
